=Description=

"This is the public collaboration wiki for the FreeMapSystem, designed to run as an open hosted service for mapping applications using free and open source software, public and copyleft geographic data, and community information anywhere in the world. The FreeMapSystem is hosted by Locative Technologies in Sebastopol, California."


